title: The Mike Rosen Radio Show JAN-09-2014 THURS
description:
The Mike Rosen Radio Show JAN-09-2014 THURS............PODCAST



Thursday, January 09, 2014


Mayor Hancock Addresses The "Knockout Game"



 
 

 - 1PM Hour

1. Top ten reasons to vote Democrat. 
2. NY Knick player fined for untying opponent's shoes
      while waiting for free throw. 
3. Mike details the Governor Chris Christie controversy 
      and the media's coverage of the story. 
4. Pot not allowed at DIA.



 - 2PM Hour

Guest: Denver Mayor Michael Hancock answers 
             listeners' questions during his monthly visit with Mike.
